Class AVLTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • BST
      • BinarySearchTree
        • AVLTree
  • class AVLTree
extends BinarySearchTree
    Subclass of Binary Search Tree ADT named AVL Tree to override the basic functions of Binary Search Tree to account for the AVL Tree's rotation.
